results.name: Greatest common divisor of product of divisors of n and product of non-divisors < n.
link: Reinhard Zumkeller, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
mathematica: a[n_] := (dd = Divisors[n]; GCD[Times @@ dd, Times @@ Complement[Range[n], dd]]); Array[a, 59]
results.author: _Reinhard Zumkeller_, Jul 29 2002
